    "But h is also ρ-equivariant since the action of ρ on SL n (R)/ SO(n) ≃ PSL n (R)/PSO(n) factors through SL n (R).By Theorem 4.3, there is a unique metric g B ∈ c such that (g B, ρ, h) solves the twisted harmonic-Einstein equations.",
